This project is an **AI Social Media Co-Pilot** that helps an older, non-technical client plan and publish TikTok and Instagram content.

The app should:
- Turn simple ideas or prompts into **scripts + captions** using **Google Gemini 3.0 Pro** (model: `gemini-3-pro-preview`).
- Generate custom visual assets using **Nano Banana Pro** (Gemini 3.0 Pro Image, model: `gemini-3-pro-image-preview`).
- Trigger basic **short-form video renders**.
- Prepare and optionally **schedule posts** via APIs.

## Core Goals

- Keep the UX **simple and forgiving** for an older user.
- Centralize all logic in a **React + FastAPI** app.
- Use external APIs for:
  - AI text & image generation (Google Gemini 3.0 Pro / Nano Banana Pro via `google-genai` SDK)
  - Video rendering (Creatomate)
  - Social publishing (Ayrshare)
- Package everything in a **single Docker image** and deploy via **Coolify**.